      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Save Facility: Simplified Interface\n\nImplement a cleaner save/home flow around user intent.\n\nPrimary question:\n\n**Where should this graph live?**\n\nThe UI should hide storage mechanics until the user chooses a destination.\n\nCore destinations:\n\n- **Local**: private, stored on this device\n- **GitHub**: durable, versioned, shareable repository storage\n- **Twilite Cloud**: future hosted/collaborative paid tier\n\nGoal: make saving feel like choosing a home for the graph, not configuring backend storage.",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "html": "",
        "svg": "",
        "visibilityRole": "browser",
        "_placement": {
          "version": 1,
          "state": "auto-placed",
          "source": "layout",
          "updatedAt": 1777653957028,
          "reason": "auto-layout"
        }
      }
    },
