      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Modal Step 1: Choose Home\n\nTitle:\n\n**Where should this graph live?**\n\nRule: if the graph is **unbound** (no durable home yet), the primary **Save** action must *always* land here. It must not write back to any previous destination implicitly.\n\nShow three large destination cards:\n\n## Local\nPrivate, stored on this device.\n\nButton: **Save Locally**\n\n## GitHub\nSave to a repository.\n\nButton: **Choose Repository**\n\n## Twilite Cloud\nHosted, collaborative graphs.\n\nButton: **Coming Soon** or disabled until paid tier exists.\n\nKeep this first step simple. No repo picker, branch selector, or visibility toggle yet.\n\nAlso show a small **Current location** chip on the toolbar at all times so users always know where future Save actions will write.",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "html": "",
        "svg": "",
        "visibilityRole": "browser",
        "_placement": {
          "version": 1,
          "state": "auto-placed",
          "source": "layout",
          "updatedAt": 1777653957028,
          "reason": "auto-layout"
        }
      }
    },
