      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Modal Step 2: GitHub Details\n\nOnly show this after the user chooses GitHub.\n\nRequired fields:\n\n- Repository picker\n- File path / graph file name\n- Save target summary\n\nCritical toggle:\n\n- **Set this as the graph home** (default ON when invoked from Save)\n  - OFF means **Save As / Export copy** (write a copy without changing the home)\n\nUseful controls:\n\n- Search repos\n- Create new repo or choose existing repo\n- Public/private visibility only when creating a repo\n\nAdvanced collapsed section:\n\n- branch\n- commit message\n\nGuardrail:\n\n- If the target is a protected file (e.g. `twilite-zone/*:root.node`), require an explicit confirmation before overwrite.\n\nFinal button:\n\n**Save to GitHub**",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "html": "",
        "svg": "",
        "visibilityRole": "browser",
        "_placement": {
          "version": 1,
          "state": "auto-placed",
