      ],
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Home vs Save As\n\nSeparate these concepts clearly.\n\n## Home\nThe graph's default write location.\n\nFuture saves go here automatically.\n\n## Save As / Export\nCreates a copy somewhere else.\n\nDoes **not** change the graph home unless the user explicitly chooses that.\n\nUI wording should reflect intent:\n\n- **Save Graph** = sets/uses Home\n- **Export copy** / **Save As** = writes a copy, does not change Home",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "html": "",
        "svg": "",
        "visibilityRole": "browser",
        "_placement": {
          "version": 1,
          "state": "auto-placed",
          "source": "layout",
          "updatedAt": 1777653957028,
          "reason": "auto-layout"
        }
      }
    },
