      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Suggested State Model\n\nTrack the graph's persistence state explicitly.\n\nPossible fields:\n\n`js\nhome: {\n  kind: 'local' | 'github' | 'twilite-cloud',\n  label: string,\n  writable: boolean,\n  ref?: string,\n  repo?: string,\n  owner?: string,\n  branch?: string,\n  path?: string,\n  visibility?: 'public' | 'private',\n  lastSavedAt?: string\n}\n`\n\nAlso track transient modal state separately:\n\n`js\nsaveFlow: {\n  step: 'choose-home' | 'github-details' | 'confirm',\n  selectedKind?: 'local' | 'github' | 'twilite-cloud'\n}\n`",
        "memo": "",
