      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Copy Improvements\n\nReplace system-heavy labels with human labels.\n\n## Current\n- Change Home\n- Current Home\n- Destination\n- Set GitHub Home\n- Save writes back to the GitHub graph URL shown above\n\n## Suggested\n- Save Graph\n- Current location\n- Choose where this graph lives\n- Save to GitHub\n- Future changes will be saved directly to this GitHub file\n- Export copy (does not change where Save writes)\n\nTone: clear, calm, confidence-building.",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "html": "",
        "svg": "",
        "visibilityRole": "browser",
        "_placement": {
          "version": 1,
          "state": "auto-placed",
          "source": "layout",
          "updatedAt": 1777653957028,
          "reason": "auto-layout"
        }
      }
