      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Success Confirmation\n\nAfter saving or setting home, show a concise confirmation.\n\nExample:\n\n**Saved to GitHub**\n\n`twilite-zone/public/root.node`\n\nFuture changes will be saved here automatically.\n\nAlso consider showing:\n\n- writable/read-only status\n- last saved time\n- link/copy action\n- open in GitHub action",
