      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Implementation Tasks for Codex\n\n1. Rename/refactor current save dialog toward **Save Graph** or **Choose Graph Home**.\n\n2. Replace first screen with destination cards:\n   - Local\n   - GitHub\n   - Twilite Cloud disabled/future\n\n3. Collapse GitHub Work / Private / Public into one GitHub destination.\n\n4. Move repo, branch, visibility, and file path controls into a GitHub-only second step.\n\n5. Add clear distinction between:\n   - set graph home\n   - save as / export copy\n\n6. Add confirmation state after save.\n\n7. Preserve existing save behavior while changing the interaction model.\n\n8. Keep advanced controls available but hidden by default.",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "html": "",
        "svg": "",
        "visibilityRole": "browser",
        "_placement": {
          "version": 1,
